node.text: I am so excited for this sale tomorrow. Please share this with everyone you can think of. I’ll be up all night color matching so let me know how I can help. If you need a color match comment color. If you need help with skincare drop skin in the comments.

node.text: On the road headed home. The goodbyes don’t get any easier for me. Some may not understand our family dynamic but we are close. I love my people hard. @whats_the_pointnshoot we keep telling you but I have to say it again. I am proud of you and can’t wait to see what you do in this world. It’s an honor to be your mom. Have a great year and don’t forget to make good decisions. #motherandson #family #proudmom #appstate #growingup #collegelife #boonenc
